  "3034680": {
    "name": "BattleCards Saga",
    "steam_appid": 3034680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/68dd7a5669000a0a96f72c0ba5d4dda5.avif?t=1738933180\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras_big/68dd7a5669000a0a96f72c0ba5d4dda5.avif?t=1738933180 width=800 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/3ed6766bcdd5e51b1e28255140e7a162.avif?t=1738933180\" width=626 height=165 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>BattleCards Saga</strong> 的世界，在这里，战略深度与宁静的氛围在一个引人入胜的自动战斗卡牌游戏中融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>选牌和团队构建</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/c0c9152aaf693d0f4e19a2e881624a53.poster.avif?t=1738933180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/c0c9152aaf693d0f4e19a2e881624a53.webm?t=1738933180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/c0c9152aaf693d0f4e19a2e881624a53.mp4?t=1738933180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战略性地从 700 多张独特插图的卡牌中进行选择，打造你的终极团队。结合不同物种，创造强大的混合体，开启新的战略可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞技场战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在竞技场中挑战自己，战术决策决定胜负。每场战斗都考验你适应和优化策略的能力，利用你的混合生物进行融合和部署。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>持续优化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>BattleCards Saga</strong> 中，优化是关键。重返战斗，调整你的方法，尝试不同的组合，发现最有效的方式来主宰比赛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/ad2031c9275e0ebfbb1f931168e36008.poster.avif?t=1738933180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/ad2031c9275e0ebfbb1f931168e36008.webm?t=1738933180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034680/extras/ad2031c9275e0ebfbb1f931168e36008.mp4?t=1738933180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收藏和融合</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次卡牌融合不仅能增强你的团队，还会为你的收藏增添一幅精美的插图。目标是发现并拥有每个生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>详细统计</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过每张卡牌的广泛统计数据深入参与游戏的元素。掌握这些数据对制定能够在竞技场中赢得胜利的策略至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神秘、禅意的宇宙</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏设置在一个神秘而宁静的宇宙中，提供了一个放松但具有挑战性的环境。这个背景增强了战略游戏体验，是那些在宁静环境中享受复杂性的玩家的完美逃避。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名独立开发者的首个项目开发，这款游戏展示了对创造的奉献和热情。将每一个挑战视为学习机会，开发者致力于优化和提升玩家体验，使 <strong>BattleCards Saga</strong> 不仅仅是一款游戏，而是一段美丽的演变体验，等待被发现。</p>",
